- This Project is a Spring Boot Project for investment
- This is a backend project and the frontend project is on './../invest-fe'
- The Frontend Project will be on Netlify.
- The Backend Project will be on Render.
- The Database will be on Supa-base
- The stock data is from Yahoo Finance API
- I can get user with only ID,
- We don't save stock's data, but we have User Table with have money, Save History, Transaction History of Save money or stock.

1. User can login with only ID and get money user has.
2. User can see stock's semi-realtime price.
3. stock's semi-realtime price is saved in only server's memory with a singleton instance.
4. User can buy or sell the stock limited user's money or stock the user has.
5. User can add or minus money with the button.
6. User can see the money with money + stock's value, and percent of the user has earned, or lost.
7. User can see the filtered data that manually added or minus of money and sell or buy stock transaction history.
